-- 7. Gillingham × Digital Marketing
INSERT INTO public.local_content (service_slug, town_slug, intro_paragraph, local_context, competition_landscape, success_approach, local_stats, pain_points, solutions, faqs, layout_variant)
VALUES (
  'digital-marketing',
  'gillingham',
  'Gillingham''s population of over one hundred and five thousand makes it one of the largest addressable local markets in Kent, yet digital marketing investment among Gillingham businesses is remarkably low. The mathematics are straightforward: a large, dense population means high search volumes and substantial social media audiences. Every pound spent on targeted digital marketing reaches more potential customers per pound than in almost any other Kent town. A Google Ads campaign targeting Gillingham plumbing services reaches an audience several times larger than the same campaign in a smaller town, at comparable cost-per-click rates. Social advertising on Facebook and Instagram can reach tens of thousands of Gillingham and Rainham residents with precision targeting. The businesses that invest in digital marketing in this market grow faster than those that do not. We build campaigns specifically for Gillingham''s large, active market.',
  'Gillingham''s digital marketing environment is defined by scale and density. The large residential population generates high search volumes across every service category. The commuter demographic using Gillingham station is reachable through timed campaigns during travel hours. The Strand attracts entertainment seekers targetable through leisure-interest advertising. Hempstead Valley shoppers can be reached through location-based campaigns. The broader Medway conurbation extends the addressable audience to nearly three hundred thousand. Facebook advertising benefits from the active community group culture that primes residents to engage with local business content.',
  'Paid digital marketing among Gillingham businesses is minimal. A handful of larger firms run Google Ads, and some restaurants near The Strand experiment with social advertising, but the vast majority of the market is uncontested. This means advertising costs are lower than they would be in a market with more sophisticated competition. Gillingham businesses willing to invest in targeted campaigns face remarkably little paid competition.',
  'We build Gillingham digital marketing campaigns around the volume opportunity. Google Ads capture the high-intent searches this large population generates daily. Social campaigns build awareness and consideration among the precise demographics most likely to need your services. Remarketing follows up with website visitors who did not convert. Every campaign is measured against real business outcomes: enquiries, calls, and revenue.',
  '{"population": 105000, "business_districts": ["Gillingham High Street", "The Strand", "Hempstead Valley Shopping Centre", "Rainham"], "key_fact": "One of Kent''s largest addressable local markets with minimal paid digital competition"}',
  '[{"title": "Gillingham''s large market untapped by paid digital channels", "description": "A town of over one hundred thousand residents generates enormous daily search volume and social media activity. Businesses relying solely on organic visibility and word of mouth access only a fraction of this addressable market. Competitors who invest even modestly in digital marketing capture customers that organic-only businesses never reach."}, {"title": "Wasted marketing spend on broad, untargeted campaigns", "description": "Some Gillingham businesses experiment with digital marketing but target too broadly, burning budget on clicks from outside their service area or from audiences unlikely to convert. Without proper geographic targeting and audience segmentation, marketing spend generates impressions rather than enquiries."}, {"title": "No remarketing strategy for Gillingham website visitors", "description": "Hundreds of Gillingham residents visit your website monthly and leave without converting. Without remarketing campaigns that follow these visitors across Google and social media, each unconverted visitor is lost permanently. In a market this large, the remarketing audience alone represents a significant untapped revenue source."}]',
  '[{"title": "Volume-optimised Google Ads for Gillingham''s large market", "description": "We build Google Ads campaigns that capture the high-volume searches Gillingham''s population generates. Keyword targeting covers both Gillingham-specific and Medway-wide terms. Geographic bid adjustments prioritise the highest-value areas. Ad copy references local landmarks and areas for maximum relevance and click-through rates."}, {"title": "Precision social advertising reaching Gillingham demographics", "description": "Facebook and Instagram campaigns target Gillingham and Rainham residents by age, household type, interests, and behaviour. A Gillingham kitchen fitter reaches homeowners in specific postcodes. A restaurant near The Strand reaches local residents interested in dining out. Precision targeting ensures every pound reaches a potential customer."}, {"title": "Remarketing campaigns converting Gillingham''s unconverted visitors", "description": "Website visitors from Gillingham who did not enquire see targeted follow-up ads across Google, Facebook, and Instagram. The plumber they considered yesterday appears in their Facebook feed today. The restaurant they browsed last week shows a booking prompt. Remarketing converts the traffic your site already receives."}]',
  '[{"question": "How much should a Gillingham business spend on digital marketing?", "answer": "Gillingham''s large market and low paid competition mean budgets go further here than in most Kent towns. Most businesses start effectively with a few hundred pounds monthly, scaling based on results. We optimise campaigns continuously to improve cost per enquiry, ensuring your budget generates maximum return."}, {"question": "Which digital platforms work best for Gillingham businesses?", "answer": "Google Ads captures high-intent searches from residents actively looking for your services. Facebook works exceptionally well given Gillingham''s active community culture. Instagram reaches the younger demographic and supports hospitality businesses. We recommend the platform mix that matches your specific customer base."}, {"question": "Can I target specific areas like Rainham within Gillingham?", "answer": "Yes. We use postcode-level geographic targeting to focus your budget on the specific areas most relevant to your business. A Gillingham tradesperson can target Rainham, Hempstead, and specific residential zones independently. Budget allocation follows where your most valuable customers are located."}, {"question": "How do I know if my Gillingham marketing campaigns are working?", "answer": "We provide monthly reporting showing exactly how many enquiries, calls, and customers each campaign generated. No vanity metrics. You see which campaigns drove real business from Gillingham and Rainham, what each lead cost, and where to increase or adjust spend for better results."}]',
  'lead-gen'
)
